dct_title_s: A map of the country from Rariton River in East Jersey to Elk Head in Maryland : shewing the several operations of the American and British armies, in 1776 & 1777
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. In upper margin: Engraved for Washington's life. From : Atlas to accompany John Marshall's The life of George Washington. Philadelphia, 1804-1807. (plate V).
